---

## Risk & Mitigation

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| Rich library adds bloat | Lock to single version, no sub-deps |
| TTY detection platform-specific | Test on Linux/macOS/Windows |
| Refresh loop consumes CPU | Add configurable refresh interval |
| DB lock on interventions.db | Use read-only cursor, timeout on lock |

